Locale-Text-Domain-OO version 0.07
==================================

Perl OO Interface to Uniforum Message Translation

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    version
    parent
    Safe
    Carp
    Cwd
    Encode
    DBI
    DBD::PO
    Perl6::Export::Attrs
    I18N::LangTags
    I18N::LangTagsDetect
    Tie::Sub
    Locale::Messages

